%h1 Login to JsGet Server

%p In order to add javascript libraries to JsGet Server, you just need to authenticate with a valid OpenId key.  This will only give you the right to manage the javascript library on js-get and prevent others from over-riding your library.


%form{:method => "post", :action => '/login'}
  %fieldset
    %legend Login Via OpenId
    %ul
      %li
        %label{:for => "openid_identifier"} OpenId
        %br
        %input{:id => "openid_identifier", :name => "openid_identifier", :type => "text", :class => "text"}
      %li
        %p.buttons
          %input{:type => "submit", :value => "Log In"}
